Apparat with Soap & Skin - Goodbye.

The theme song from the Netflix series 'Dark'. Watch the trailer here: https://youtu.be/zy0b9e40tK8

Taken from the album 'Devil's Walk' available on Mute: http://smarturl.it/devilswalk

Also sampled on Lupe Fiasco's "Jonylah Forever."
